A vast digital cityscape rendered in cyberpunk style, featuring dozens of identical neon-lit apartment towers arranged in a grid pattern, each tower glowing with its own distinct color - electric blue, hot pink, acid green, burning orange. Above them floats a single massive dark control station with tentacle-like cables connecting down to each tower, orchestrating from the shadows. The scene is set against a rain-soaked night sky with data streams flowing between buildings like rivers of light. Steam rises from the streets below, and holographic advertisements flicker between the structures. The perspective is from a high vantage point looking down at this organized chaos of isolated yet connected units, emphasizing both separation and unified management.
